activeauthentication
==========

This is a basic authentication generator for rails, modified from techoweenie's wonderful acts_as_authenticated [http://technoweenie.stikipad.com/plugins/show/Acts+as+Authenticated].

To use:

  ./script/generate authenticated user account

Add the following to your application.rb file:

  include AuthenticatedSystem

Add the following to your controller:

  before_filter :login_required

Be sure to fill in the properties in config active_directory.yml before using.
